AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore hughie@carrollonline.uk-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path /home/hughie/.local/share/mail/hughie@carrollonline.uk/
Inbox /home/hughie/.local/share/mail/hughie@carrollonline.uk/INBOX

Channel hughie@carrollonline.uk
Expunge Both
Far :hughie@carrollonline.uk-remote:
Near :hughie@carrollonline.uk-local:
Patterns * !"[Gmail]/All Mail"
Create Both
SyncState *
MaxMessages 0
ExpireUnread no
# End profile


